{{gherdëina}}'''Mont Sëuc''' ie l inuem de na [[furnadoia]] te [[Gherdëina]] che porta dal luech de [[Urtijëi]] sun [[Mont Sëuc]]. Plu avisa scumëncia la furnadoia te la [[frazion (Talia)|frazion]] [[Sureghes]] che toca pra l chemun de [[Ciastel (chemun)|Ciastel]]. Duta la furnadoia ie perchël tl raion dl chemun de Ciastel. Sota la furnadoia ie l [[purtoi]] ''[[Pilat (purtoi)|Pilat]]'' che porta da Mont Sëuc ju a Urtijëi.
